headline: Nasdaq to Hold Third Quarter 2025 Investor Conference Call
summary: NEW YORK, Sept. 29, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Nasdaq (Nasdaq: NDAQ) has scheduled its third quarter 2025 financial results announcement. Who:Nasdaq’s CEO, CFO, and additional members of its senior management team What:Review Nasdaq’s third quarter 2025 financial results When:Tuesday, October 21, 2025 Results Call: 8:00 AM ET Senior management will be available for questions from the investment community following prepared remarks.
